column4: Text
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "5BAA78EE433E1F3A19C1F5BF1FD9EF19", "Quit messing around!")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "9D409F7B4B12EA727360C39637E3ECF3", "Alright. I don\'t think I\'ll do it again.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "4DB3D04949586B30BEA904AA0A2BC19D", "I think this is the last room.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "60A5852F46C064BA0E5BB39D918939C5", "Which one?")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "92A1729C4B998D82EF02FFA8CCD96EB4", "That voice...sounds like WaruMonzaemon!")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "1AD9CC634957942F74BA2EA650D38D82", "A big box or a small box. I can read your mind!")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "ED06BDB44458C7215727E2A93C3D2DBB", "Huh? Aaahhhh!")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "44C41E304FFBD599DCF75EA68DC2945C", "Ha ha ha, you jerk! You missed!")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "9EC89D8F455A409861B9A4997BD44EAB", "Ohhhh, you found out! He he he. Nervous?")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "DA633D71415E76E6E27965AFFFD5420B", "Darn, what\'s so funny?")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "A242CE6D43C23E8F0C2666B82CA47311", "Wow, don\'t get excited. Why are you here today? Do you want to work for me?")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "922EDECE4362D82A770CABAA145667A1", "Give us back my friend you kidnapped!")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "B2FB225C473DA24038C02990291B6F59", "Friend? What are you talking about. Do I look like I would do such a thing?")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "23878E764169164D85FA6CA5D465EB4D", "Yeah!")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "084435C4478082FA312EC1A0430D6740", "Wow, you\'re correct again! Yes, I\'m the one! I did it!")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "008247934D9E03C4E1240A8287517639", "But you know you can\'t have him back. Because I\'m WaruMonzaemon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "101BE6D34B67BB8B1F55F886746BB134", "If that\'s what you think, I\'ll force you!")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "2F21976A439306F997CEBCBF2FD85729", "Are you kidding? You are going to defeat me?")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "C9418F534DB81AF9B8BC4984ED8D0F13", "You know what? You\'d better wake up and face reality!")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "0E0B2BFD4CA492A7B54769B66430F6FC", "Hey, give me back my friend you kidnapped.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "3DA7F90C455151604B2710BC0931BB7F", "Ugghhh....no way! I can\'t believe it, I\'m losing....")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "F5B5F2464CC85CA8EC22A1A89F9FB295", "Come on!")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "BD8F57EA4BDE45497C6D1DA91EA83841", "Well... I guess I don\'t have choice. Here.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "3BB58297420E6A61F395DCA0E3A923C0", "Hey, stop goofing off, that\'s enough!")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "A72145AA4EA80D5E6957EB942B4F68FD", "Hey, don\'t you get the joke? Here. This is the one.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "C22D56C74E4F8D5E571C438D2A486FB5", "What is this? This is a Gear.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "53A5B4B940E4AB09FBEC6AA8CA1855C4", "Yeah, that\'s right.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "437299DE444B23DFD2EC43B7DE7B7342", "This is the friend???")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "A1EA32964F93E65AF2F8FFB576805F58", "Well, I didn\'t take anything else. Really.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "BB0761EF4D1A483BBE0AF2B65D9922A2", "I guess I\'ll take this back for now.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "BCB6E4F544488B9DDB2D1482F74A28CE", "You! Don\'t do anything bad any more, alright?!")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "EC9104F3412464C5572469BECA04B157", "Alright. I don\'t think it will happen again.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "7AD6C83E457F4C11680926A54F4B02B5", "Somehow I don\'t believe you, but I have so much stuff to take care of.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "00729F8046CB274B615BBA884EF1A1C3", "Oh no, I have too many Items. I have to throw one away.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E437DE74ED99E50F9CF8BACB605057F]", "054169914A98CC6A7B2BF693AB75A48A", "I got a <Item>Gear</>!")
